# Alur Kerja Sistem: ACS Intelligence Assistant

Dokumen ini menjelaskan **arsitektur** dan **alur kerja** lengkap dari sistem ACS Intelligence Assistant — mulai dari pengguna mengetik pertanyaan hingga jawaban ditampilkan di layar.

---

## 1. Arsitektur Umum (High-Level)

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph FRONTEND["🖥️ Frontend (Next.js)"]
        UI["User Interface"]
        Hooks["Custom Hooks<br/>(useChat, useRAG)"]
        Types["Types (chat.ts)"]
    end

    subgraph BACKEND["⚙️ Backend (Express.js)"]
        MW["Middleware<br/>(Auth + Classification)"]
        Routes["Routes<br/>(auth, chat, rag)"]
        Controllers["Controllers<br/>(auth, chat, rag)"]
        Services["Services Layer<br/>(11 services)"]
    end

    subgraph EXTERNAL["🌐 External Services"]
        Groq["Groq API<br/>(Llama 3.3 70B)"]
        ES["Elasticsearch<br/>(Vector Search)"]
        PG["PostgreSQL<br/>(Prisma ORM)"]
    end

    UI --> Hooks
    Hooks --> Routes
    Routes --> MW --> Controllers --> Services
    Services --> Groq
    Services --> ES
    Services --> PG
```

---

## 2. Alur Autentikasi

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant AUTH as /api/auth
    participant MW as Auth Middleware
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Masukkan username & password
    FE->>AUTH: POST /api/auth/login
    AUTH->>DB: Cek kredensial (bcrypt)
    DB-->>AUTH: User data
    AUTH-->>FE: { accessToken, refreshToken }
    FE->>FE: Simpan token di localStorage

    Note over FE,MW: Setiap request selanjutnya...

    FE->>MW: Request + Bearer Token
    MW->>MW: Verify JWT
    MW->>MW: Set req.user & req.classification
    MW-->>FE: ✅ Authorized / ❌ 401
```

| Endpoint | Method | Fungsi |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/auth/login` | POST | Login, dapat access & refresh token |
| `/api/auth/refresh` | POST | Refresh access token |
| `/api/auth/profile` | GET | Ambil data user saat ini |
| `/api/auth/logout` | POST | Logout + blacklist token |
| `/api/auth/verify` | GET | Verifikasi validitas token |
| `/api/auth/users` | GET | Daftar semua user (admin) |

---

## 3. Alur Chat / Query AI

Ini adalah **alur utama** saat pengguna mengajukan pertanyaan.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["👤 User mengetik pertanyaan"] --> B{Mode yang dipilih?}

    B -->|Q&A / Summary| C["POST /api/chat/advanced-query"]
    B -->|Enhanced Visual| D["POST /api/chat/universal-visual"]
    B -->|Ontology| E["POST /api/chat/ontology"]
    B -->|Strategic| F["POST /api/chat/strategic-analysis"]

    C --> G["chatController.advancedQuery"]
    D --> H["chatController.universalVisual"]
    E --> I["chatController.ontology"]
    F --> J["chatController.strategicAnalysis"]

    G --> K["Services Layer"]
    H --> K
    I --> K
    J --> K

    K --> L["ragService.query()<br/>Cari konteks dari dokumen"]
    K --> M["aiService<br/>Kirim ke Groq LLM"]
    K --> N["visualAnalysisService<br/>Generate visualisasi"]
    K --> O["ontologyService<br/>Ekstrak entitas & relasi"]

    L --> P["Elasticsearch<br/>(Vector Search)"]
    M --> Q["Groq API<br/>(Llama 3.3 70B)"]

    P --> R["Context Merger"]
    Q --> R
    N --> R
    O --> R

    R --> S["Response + Visualisasi + Sources"]
    S --> T["👤 User melihat jawaban"]
```

### Detail Endpoint Chat

| Endpoint | Fungsi | Service Utama |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/chat/advanced-query` | Analisis teks lanjutan + security scan | ai, rag, processor |
| `/api/chat/universal-visual` | Analisis visual + Elasticsearch data | visual-analysis, rag |
| `/api/chat/ontology` | Knowledge graph & entity extraction | ontology, rag |
| `/api/chat/strategic-analysis` | SWOT, threat matrix, fishbone | visual-analysis, rag |
| `/api/chat/smart-query` | Auto-detect tipe analisis | ai, visual-analysis |
| `/api/chat/visual-request` | Request visualisasi spesifik | visual-analysis |
| `/api/chat/quick-visual` | Visualisasi cepat dari topik | visual-analysis |
| `/api/chat/query` | Query dasar RAG | rag, ai, processor |

---

## 4. Alur RAG (Document Upload & Retrieval)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend (useRAG)
    participant API as /api/rag
    participant RAG as ragController
    participant ES as Elasticsearch
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over U,DB: 📤 Upload Dokumen

    U->>FE: Pilih file (PDF/TXT)
    FE->>API: POST /api/rag/documents (multipart)
    API->>RAG: uploadDocuments()
    RAG->>RAG: Parse & chunk dokumen
    RAG->>ES: Index chunks + embeddings
    RAG->>DB: Simpan metadata dokumen
    RAG-->>FE: ✅ Upload berhasil

    Note over U,DB: 🔍 Pencarian Konteks (saat Query)

    FE->>API: ragService.query(question)
    API->>ES: Vector similarity search
    ES-->>API: Top-K relevant chunks
    API-->>FE: Konteks dokumen + skor relevansi
```

| Endpoint | Method | Fungsi |
|---|---|---|
| `/api/rag/documents` | POST | Upload dokumen (PDF/TXT, max 10MB) |
| `/api/rag/documents/uploaded` | GET | Daftar dokumen yang sudah diupload |
| `/api/rag/documents/:id` | DELETE | Hapus dokumen |
| `/api/rag/search` | GET | Cari dokumen berdasarkan query |
| `/api/rag/index-info` | GET | Info index Elasticsearch |

---

## 5. Alur Security & Classification

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A["Request masuk"] --> B["Auth Middleware"]
    B --> C{Token valid?}
    C -->|Tidak| D["❌ 401 Unauthorized"]
    C -->|Ya| E["Set req.user"]
    E --> F["Classification Middleware"]
    F --> G{Role & Clearance}
    G -->|Publik| H["Akses: Publik saja"]
    G -->|Internal| I["Akses: Publik + Internal"]
    G -->|Terbatas| J["Akses: + Terbatas"]
    G -->|Rahasia| K["Akses: Semua level"]
    H & I & J & K --> L["Controller menerima request"]
    L --> M["PII Masking"]
    M --> N["Security Scan"]
    N --> O["Response ke User"]
```

### Level Klasifikasi Dokumen

| Level | Warna | Siapa yang boleh akses |
|---|---|---|
| **Rahasia** | 🔴 Merah | Admin saja |
| **Terbatas** | 🟠 Oranye | Analyst + Admin |
| **Internal** | 🟡 Kuning | User + Analyst + Admin |
| **Publik** | 🟢 Hijau | Semua pengguna |

---

## 6. Layer Services

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Controllers
        CC["chatController"]
        AC["authController"]
        RC["ragController"]
    end

    subgraph Services["Services (11 files)"]
        AI["ai.service<br/>(Groq LLM)"]
        RAG["rag.service<br/>(Document retrieval)"]
        VA["visual-analysis.service<br/>(Visualisasi)"]
        ONT["ontology.service<br/>(Knowledge Graph)"]
        AUTH["auth.service<br/>(JWT + bcrypt)"]
        CLS["classification.service<br/>(Tingkat keamanan)"]
        POL["policy-analysis.service<br/>(Analisis kebijakan)"]
        QC["query-classifier.service<br/>(Klasifikasi query)"]
        PROC["processor.service<br/>(Post-processing)"]
        SEARCH["search.service<br/>(Pencarian)"]
        TOOL["tool-calling.service<br/>(Tool calling)"]
    end

    CC --> AI & RAG & VA & ONT & PROC & SEARCH & TOOL & QC & POL
    AC --> AUTH
    RC --> RAG
```

---

## 7. Technology Stack

| Layer | Teknologi |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | Next.js 14 (App Router), React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS |
| **Backend** | Express.js, Node.js |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL + Prisma ORM |
| **Search Engine** | Elasticsearch (vector search + full-text) |
| **AI/LLM** | Groq API → Llama 3.3 70B Versatile |
| **Auth** | JWT (access + refresh tokens), bcrypt |
| **File Upload** | Multer (memory storage, max 10MB) |
| **Security** | Helmet, CORS, PII masking, security scan |

---

## 8. Ringkasan Folder Project

```
acs-master/ (Backend)
├── index.js              # Entry point + global middleware
├── middleware/
│   └── auth.middleware.js # JWT + classification guard
├── routes/
│   ├── auth.routes.js     # Auth endpoints
│   ├── chat.js            # Chat endpoints → chatController
│   └── rag.js             # RAG endpoints → ragController
├── controllers/
│   ├── auth.controller.js # Login, logout, profile
│   ├── chat.controller.js # Visual, query, ontology
│   └── rag.controller.js  # Upload, delete, search
├── services/ (11 files)   # Business logic layer
├── prisma/                # Database schema & migrations
└── elasticsearch/         # ES setup & configuration

bin-intelligence-assistant/ (Frontend)
├── app/
│   ├── page.tsx           # Landing page
│   ├── login/             # Login page
│   └── analyst-workspace/ # Main workspace
├── components/
│   ├── ai-model.tsx       # Main AI chat component
│   └── ui/                # Reusable UI components
├── hooks/
│   ├── useChat.ts         # Chat API state management
│   └── useRAG.ts          # RAG document management
└── types/
    └── chat.ts            # Shared TypeScript interfaces
```
